DWFToolkit::DWFContentElementPropertyVisitor

DWFToolkit::DWFContentElementPropertyVisitor Class Reference
[DWF Publisher API]

#include "dwf/publisher/impl/ContentElementPropertyVisitor.h"

Detailed Description

An implementation for objects (visitors) that publishers can use with publishable sources to extract their property data. This implementation is used for working with content elements available since DWF toolkit version 7.2.

Since:
7.2.0
